                {
                    "id": "e6ef63fffdb94bcdab2bc",
                    "stepText": "Finally, use the total mechanical energy formula for circular orbits to calculate the total energy $!$E$!$. Combine the numerator and denominator computed in the previous steps and ensure you include the negative sign in the formula. What is the resulting energy required for the satellite?",
